\c 52
\s Akaipa ngaarege kuva namanyawi
\s nokuti Jehovha anochengeta vanhu vake vakarurama
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Rwiyo rweMashiri rwaDhavhidhi,. panguva yakasvika Dhoegi muEdhomu akaudza Sauro, achiti, "Dhavhidhi asvika paimba yaAhimereki."
\p
\v 1 Unozvirumbidzireiko nezvakashata, iwe mhare? Tsitsi dzaMwari dziripo misi yose.
\v 2 Rurimi rwako runofunga kutaura zvakaipa; Rwakafanana nechisvo chinopinza, ruchiita zvinonyengera.
\v 3 Unoda zvakaipa kupfuura zvakanaka; Nokureva nhema kupfuura kutaura zvakarurama.
\v 4 Unoda mashoko ose okuparadza, Iwe rurimi runonyengera.
\v 5 Mwari achakuparadzawo saizvozvo nokusingaperi, Achakubata akakubvisa patende rako, th(ukudzura panyika yavapenyu.
\v 6 Vakarurama vachazviona vakatya, Vachamuseka, vachiti,
\v 7 "Tarirai, hoyu munhu asina kuita Mwari nhare yake, Asi akavimba nokuwanda kwepfuma yake,
\s Akazvisimbisa pazvakaipa zvake."
\p
\v 8 Asi kana ndirini, ndakafanana nomuorivhi munyoro muimba yaMwari;
\s Ndinovimba netsitsi dzaMwari nokusingaperi-peri.
\p
\v 9 Ndichakuvongai nokusingaperi, nokuti
\s ndimi makazviita;
\s Ndichamirira zita renyu pamberi pavatsvene
\s venyu nokuti rakanaka.
